```python id=bloq
from qualtran.bloqs.mcmt import MultiControlX
bloq = MultiControlX(cvs=(1,) * 5)
```
```python id=golden
import numpy as np
# C5X: control=first 5 qubits (MSB), target=last (big-endian). flip target iff all controls 1.
golden = np.zeros((1<<6, 1<<6), dtype=complex)
for s in range(1<<6):
    o = (s ^ 1) if (s >> 1) == ((1<<5) - 1) else s
    golden[o, s] = 1
```
